query:
INSERT INTO poll_option (
                    id,
                    poll_id,
                    option_text,
                    is_write_in
                ) VALUES (
                    $1,
                    $2,
                    $3,
                    $4
                ) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
                    option_text = EXCLUDED.option_text,
                    is_write_in = EXCLUDED.is_write_in
